nodes.text: Quinny was a male Besalisk who worked as a bartender on an unspecified bar. He was friendly with Connor Freeman—a Human who regularly slept on his counter—and would often look out for him.

At one point, a certain Gand bounty hunter came to the bar and tried to collect the bounty that Tayand—a powerful crimelord Freeman owed credits to—placed on Freeman. Quinny helped Freeman by subtly handing him a blaster, which Freeman used to shoot the bounty hunter. When Freeman was about to leave, Quinny reminded him to dispose of the dead body.
